        "top_heading": "True beauty comes from within: Roberto Coin knows this well and has made it a motto and a guiding principle in his personal life and in the company.",
        "top_text": "<p>In fact, Roberto Coin is a member of the most important organizations active in promoting responsible practices throughout the entire supply chain, from raw material sourcing to production, trading and retail: the Responsible Jewellery Council (RJC), the World Diamond Council, and CIBJO (The World Jewelry Confederation), among the others.</p>",
        "top_image": "shopify://shop_images/roberto-coin-authentic-beauty-img2-1024x683.jpg",
        "full_image": "shopify://shop_images/roberto-coin-authentic-beauty-img3.png",
        "center_text": "<p>As a company and as a brand, Roberto Coin is committed daily to the highest standards of ethical, social, environmental behavior and respect for human rights, <strong>to deliver jewelry that shines a true and good light into your hands.</strong></p><p>All materials used in Roberto Coin jewelry come from certified and responsible sources. Diamonds come only from legitimate, conflict-free sources that are certified by the Kimberley Process Certification Scheme (KPCS). This is an international system of certification and warranties founded by the World Diamond Council itself, where Roberto Coin is an active member of the Board of Directors.</p>",
